Business Development Executive - PT Bank ANZ Indonesia
Business Development Executive  -
Business Development Executive
Responsibilities
The Business Development Executive will conduct daily and weekly planning of prospecting/sales activities in order to reach targets and acquire new signature priority customer. This can be achieved through various avenues; call – introduction and appointment scheduling, visit – product and services presentation, follow up – determine interest level and closing the deal. You will develop strong networks and relationship with prospective clients. All sales activities must be done in compliance with company and government regulations and policies. Requirements:Hold a minimum of Bachelor degree from a reputable UniversityMinimum 1 year experience from diverse industries with sales and service oriented background and professions including but not limited to banking, insurance, propertyExcellent communication and presentation skillStrong passion in sales and good network with high end societiesGood knowledge of basic banking products will be a plus point Due to Indonesia's current legislative requirements, this role is only open to Indonesian nationals. This is an opportunity to undertake a role offering exceptional opportunities for professional development with a broad range of career paths. It’s a place where the determined can succeed, the willing can grow and together, we can prosper. We connect you to your world of opportunity.
